204
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:16,720
Itulah tempat yang kita cari.

205
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,650
Macam mana awak tahu pintu akan terbuka?

206
00:17:19,650 --> 00:17:20,550
Saya teka saja.

207
00:17:23,569 --> 00:17:25,770
Kalau begitu, nak letakkan apa di sini?

208
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,730
Apa benda yang awak pegang itu?

209
00:17:39,870 --> 00:17:41,270
Cuaca hari ini agak baik.

210
00:17:42,840 --> 00:17:44,300
Sekejap lagi bersedia...

211
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:46,410
Ini anak kapal punya patung dewa.

212
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:48,090
Kalau awak ambil, mereka akan merusuh!

213
00:17:48,090 --> 00:17:49,670
Janganlah cakap sampai begitu serius.

214
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:50,610
Awak dengar cakap saya.

215
00:17:50,610 --> 00:17:52,500
Saya dah lama kenal dengan benda ini,

216
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,180
