217
00:17:54,180 --> 00:17:55,110
Mari, beri saya.

218
00:17:55,530 --> 00:17:58,270
Sekarang saya tahan awak
atas tuduhan mencuri barang

219
00:17:58,270 --> 00:17:59,070
